---
import "animate.css";
import Footer from "./Footer.astro";
---

<section
  class="relative min-h-[100vh] w-full flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-20 overflow-hidden"
>
  <div
    class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl w-full text-center flex flex-col items-center animate__animated animate__fadeIn"
  >
    <h1
      class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl font-bold mb-8 drop-shadow-lg animate__animated animate__fadeInDown"
    >
      <span class="text-blue-500">
        Tu ventaja en apuestas deportivas:
      </span>
      <br />
      <span class="text-purple-500">
        análisis y valor
      </span>
    </h1>
    <p
      class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-800 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 font-medium animate__animated animate__fadeInUp"
    >
      Análisis profesional, métodos estadísticos rentables y ligas seleccionadas
      por su fiabilidad. Descubre los partidos con mayor probabilidad y valor
    </p>
    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-14 w-full animate__animated animate__zoomIn"
    >
      <!-- Tarjeta 1 -->
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 p-6 bg-white/90 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-blue-500 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-xl transition-transform duration-200"
      >
        <div
          class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-400 mb-2"
        >
          <i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line text-white text-2xl"></i>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-800 text-base font-semibold">
          Probabilidades de cada partido y mercado, analizadas con métodos
          estadísticos verificados.
        </p>
      </div>
      <!-- Tarjeta 2 -->
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 p-6 bg-white/90 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-blue-500 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-xl transition-transform duration-200"
      >
        <div
          class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-400 mb-2"
        >
          <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved text-white text-2xl"></i>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-800 text-base font-semibold">
          Ligas seleccionadas por su fiabilidad y valor estadístico.
        </p>
      </div>
      <!-- Tarjeta 3 -->
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 p-6 bg-white/90 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-blue-500 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-xl transition-transform duration-200"
      >
        <div
          class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-400 mb-2"
        >
          <i class="fa-solid fa-star text-white text-2xl"></i>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-800 text-base font-semibold">
          Ranking de los 5 partidos más probables del día por cada método.
        </p>
      </div>
      <!-- Tarjeta 4 -->
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 p-6 bg-white/90 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-blue-500 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-xl transition-transform duration-200"
      >
        <div
          class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-400 mb-2"
        >
          <i class="fa-solid fa-heart text-white text-2xl"></i>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-800 text-base font-semibold">
          Guarda tus partidos favoritos y toma decisiones con criterio y
          confianza.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4 animate__animated animate__fadeInUp"
    >
      <a
        href="/analisis"
        class="text-white text-lg px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl font-semibold shadow-[0_5px_20px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)] bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-400 to-blue-500
         hover:from-blue-500 hover:to-purple-500
         hover:text-white
         transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out
         transform hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 active:shadow-inner"
      >
        Ver partidos analizados
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<Footer />
